For the Server::
---------------
Open a new terminal in the net Dir and type the commands needed::

   python server.py
or
   python3 server.py

Or 2 clients::
   python main.py localhost &
   python3 main.py localhost &

You can also connect on your LAN if you know the local IP address::
   python main.py <192.168.1.100>

You can run it standalone choose either one::
   python3 main.py localhost
or
   python3 main.py
